{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blogs/fileshare","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><em>Overview of Group based Peer-to-Peer file sharing system</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Multiple Trackers behind a load balancer (for fault tolerance and load balancing)</li>\n<li>Data abstraction layer (containing user management data and files metadata)</li>\n<li>Peers: interface for users to share data with in their groups\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cd162e70f28782a6e6a6fdd6ccc1b883/6219e/group_file_sharing.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"group file sharing\"\n        title=\"group file sharing\"\n        src=\"/static/cd162e70f28782a6e6a6fdd6ccc1b883/4b190/group_file_sharing.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cd162e70f28782a6e6a6fdd6ccc1b883/e07e9/group_file_sharing.jpg 200w,\n/static/cd162e70f28782a6e6a6fdd6ccc1b883/066f9/group_file_sharing.jpg 400w,\n/static/cd162e70f28782a6e6a6fdd6ccc1b883/4b190/group_file_sharing.jpg 800w,\n/static/cd162e70f28782a6e6a6fdd6ccc1b883/6219e/group_file_sharing.jpg 911w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Peer-to-Peer communication steps</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>User login to a peer and queries tracker for files available and gets their metadata containing the seeders list</li>\n<li>Requests the seeders to send the piece information</li>\n<li>Apply piece selection algorithm to optimize the data transfer between peers</li>\n<li>Actual file data transfer in pieces</li>\n<li>Notify tracker to add as seeder once the piece is available.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1d27e5aa6d8881b671eea7d38adec3f3/af5f6/dowload_steps.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"dowload steps\"\n        title=\"dowload steps\"\n        src=\"/static/1d27e5aa6d8881b671eea7d38adec3f3/4b190/dowload_steps.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1d27e5aa6d8881b671eea7d38adec3f3/e07e9/dowload_steps.jpg 200w,\n/static/1d27e5aa6d8881b671eea7d38adec3f3/066f9/dowload_steps.jpg 400w,\n/static/1d27e5aa6d8881b671eea7d38adec3f3/4b190/dowload_steps.jpg 800w,\n/static/1d27e5aa6d8881b671eea7d38adec3f3/af5f6/dowload_steps.jpg 1166w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Technical Overview</h3>\n<h4>Directory and File structure</h4>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 345px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1da1d64794911942b90dc7b2850baa1d/8d48c/code_structure_overview.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 199.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"code structure overview\"\n        title=\"code structure overview\"\n        src=\"/static/1da1d64794911942b90dc7b2850baa1d/8d48c/code_structure_overview.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1da1d64794911942b90dc7b2850baa1d/e07e9/code_structure_overview.jpg 200w,\n/static/1da1d64794911942b90dc7b2850baa1d/8d48c/code_structure_overview.jpg 345w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 345px) 100vw, 345px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4>Technical concepts</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Server Client Communication</li>\n<li>Multi threading</li>\n<li>Hashing for integrity check</li>\n<li>Piece Selection Algorithm</li>\n<li>File Access</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Dependencies</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>pthread (multithreading)</li>\n<li>crypto (hashing)</li>\n<li>jsoncpp (data exchanage format between systems)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Functional Aspects:</h4>\n<h5>User Interface Commands Representations</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Create User</li>\n<li>Login</li>\n<li>Create Group</li>\n<li>Join Group</li>\n<li>Leave Group</li>\n<li>List Pending Requests</li>\n<li>Accept Request</li>\n<li>List Groups</li>\n<li>List Files</li>\n<li>Upload File</li>\n<li>Download File</li>\n<li>Show Downloads</li>\n<li>Stop Shares</li>\n<li>Logout</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fc557e9107ff1131ab94cf6fdfa9f1a7/f2bdc/user_commands_rep.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"user commands rep\"\n        title=\"user commands rep\"\n        src=\"/static/fc557e9107ff1131ab94cf6fdfa9f1a7/4b190/user_commands_rep.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fc557e9107ff1131ab94cf6fdfa9f1a7/e07e9/user_commands_rep.jpg 200w,\n/static/fc557e9107ff1131ab94cf6fdfa9f1a7/066f9/user_commands_rep.jpg 400w,\n/static/fc557e9107ff1131ab94cf6fdfa9f1a7/4b190/user_commands_rep.jpg 800w,\n/static/fc557e9107ff1131ab94cf6fdfa9f1a7/f2bdc/user_commands_rep.jpg 834w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4>Integration aspects:</h4>\n<h5>Internal APIs as part of Download scenario</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>get<em>file</em>info -> API to get file information from tracker</li>\n<li>get<em>piece</em>info -> API to get piece information from the seeder</li>\n<li>download_piece -> API to download a particular piece</li>\n<li>update<em>seeders</em>list -> Update seeders list after piece is downloaded</li>\n<li>update_status -> update download status</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"date":"October 10, 2019","path":"/blogs/fileshare","title":"Group-based peer-to-peer file sharing system"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["1132682437","1809658638","2461565632","63159454"]}